an be best served – contrasts greatly with the conventional productcentric management model that exists at other wealth management firms we believe that only by creating an environment where  experience and knowledge are leveraged without artificial constraints and are appropriately supported by dedicated resources can we achieve superior results for our clients research process our investment team employs a multidisciplinary approach in its decisionmaking process we analyze a broad range of asset classes and  strategies and develop forward looking projections of risk and return across a number of potential scenarios those which appear most attractive and positively asymmetric direct our manager research activity where we develop and refine a thesis for investment in the asset class and determine the most effective form of implementation alternatives from simple liquid passive forms of exposure to more active and potentially less liquid ones are evaluated to identify the most  optimal approach given the thesis manager selection draws upon the team’s long history and experience and is complemented by comprehensive operational due diligence in conjunction with the firm’s chief  compliance officer once selected asset classes are combined into client portfolios based on potential risks and returns liquidity and sensitivity to various factors portfolios are constructed to minimize the chance of permanent impairment of capital and to provide attractive riskadjusted returns  throughout market cycles this process is repeated on an ongoing basis and changes made to portfolios as expectations for risk and reward  change due to fundamentals valuations and external factors hillview’s investment committee is the body responsible for setting portfolio allocations as wells as the hiring and firing of investment  managers and is comprised of the firm’s senior investment  professionals and executives prior to hiring we subject  investment managers to thorough due diligence and compliance reviews on a quarterly basis managers found in deficit of our expectations are subject to review and termination the investment culture at hillview is founded on entrepreneurial thinking and devoid of traditional institutional constraints  our experience is that the best investment opportunities often reside outside of the consensus we have a history of identifying and recommending less well known asset classes and strategies – not on the menus of institutional investors – which offered  attractive returns and opportunities for added value over time our investment process has nurtured a conviction in our investment decisions – one that has led to successful  partnerships with the individuals families and institutions we have had the privilege to serve risk management our primary objective is to avoid permanent impairment of capital we employ proprietary tools to estimate measure and manage risk across portfolios these tools were developed by our investment team in order to specifically address the unique challenges of managing multiasset portfolios similarly portfolios are constructed with the unique constraints and objectives of each client in mind our commitment is to maintain a strong compliance culture because we understand that risk management extends beyond just the investment portfolio our policy and operating committee – consisting of senior members from the investment team client service operations technology and compliance areas – meets monthly to discuss issues that may impact our clients and our business with members from every department working together we have created a flexible streamlined and open system of internal communication that undeniably leads to better results for our clients client service  report from its beginnings hillview employed a business model rooted in clientcentricity – it is embedded deep within the every fabric of our firm’s governance management practices and compensation structures the firm’s high employeetoclient ratio helps to provide a dedicated diligent service team for each of our clients each team is led by one of the firm’s partners and includes a financial planning associate who handles daytoday responsibilities and tasks resulting from client interactions and a portfolio administrator responsible for all operational functions service includes timely systematic client communication and informative meetings throughout the year we are leaders in the efficient use technology – leveraging it to enhance the client experience increase the value of our service and deepen our relationships the hillview client portal offers a performancereporting platform that aggregates information on all of a client’s investments providing portfoliowide visibility regardless of where assets are held our clients get a comprehensive view of their assets while we analyze and monitor all of their investments – enabling us to make betterinformed recommendations and advise them in a holistic manner the portal is password protected and available  providing a reliable and insightful tool for our clients to view their investments information on all liquid investments is available on a dailybasis and less liquid investments on a monthlyquarterly basis clients may also store important documents and personal information in their document vault in times of emergency they can count on knowing there is one secure location to access all the information they need hillview capital advisors llc » process process investment philosophy hillview’s investment philosophy represents the “triumph of common sense” in a crowded and challenging investment environment where we consistently pursue what is in the best interests of our clients the firm combines the research and analytical strengths of a high quality institution with the hightouch services of a multifamily office we work within a disciplined process to conceive create and manage customized wealth management solutions that endeavor to protect our clients’ assets and grow their wealth in  everchanging markets we seek investment opportunities outside of consensus are not afraid to move ahead of the crowd and will allocate capital in a manner that we believe best exploits these opportunities while managing our requirements for transparency and liquidity our extensive knowledge and experience has enabled us to consistently identify opportunities with prospects for superior returns with limited and quantifiable risk to capital in many cases these opportunities were not obvious or popular at the time but our indepth research and courage of our convictions led us to recommend investments that served our clients well hillview’s clientcentric approach – what we believe to be the only way a client can be best served – contrasts greatly with the conventional productcentric management model that exists at other wealth management firms we believe that only by creating an environment where  experience and knowledge are leveraged without artificial constraints and are appropriately supported by dedicated resources can we achieve superior results for our clients research process our investment team employs a multidisciplinary approach in its decisionmaking process we analyze a broad range of asset classes and  strategies and develop forward looking projections of risk and return across a number of potential scenarios those which appear most attractive and positively asymmetric direct our manager research activity where we develop and refine a thesis for investment in the asset class and determine the most effective form of implementation alternatives from simple liquid passive forms of exposure to more active and potentially less liquid ones are evaluated to identify the most  optimal approach given the thesis manager selection draws upon the team’s long history and experience and is complemented by comprehensive operational due diligence in conjunction with the firm’s chief  compliance officer once selected asset classes are combined into client portfolios based on potential risks and returns liquidity and sensitivity to various factors portfolios are constructed to minimize the chance of permanent impairment of capital and to provide attractive riskadjusted returns  throughout market cycles this process is repeated on an ongoing basis and changes made to portfolios as expectations for risk and reward  change due to fundamentals valuations and external factors hillview’s investment committee is the body responsible for setting portfolio allocations as wells as the hiring and firing of investment  managers and is comprised of the firm’s senior investment  professionals and executives prior to hiring we subject  investment managers to thorough due diligence and compliance reviews on a quarterly basis managers found in deficit of our expectations are subject to review and termination the investment culture at hillview is founded on entrepreneurial thinking and devoid of traditional institutional constraints  our experience is that the best investment opportunities often reside outside of the consensus we have a history of identifying and recommending less well known asset classes and strategies – not on the menus of institutional investors – which offered  attractive returns and opportunities for added value over time our investment process has nurtured a conviction in our investment decisions – one that has led to successful  partnerships with the individuals families and institutions we have had the privilege to serve risk management our primary objective is to avoid permanent impairment of capital we employ proprietary tools to estimate measure and manage risk across portfolios these tools were developed by our investment team in order to specifically address the unique challenges of managing multiasset portfolios similarly portfolios are constructed with the unique constraints and objectives of each client in mind our commitment is to maintain a strong compliance culture because we understand that risk management extends beyond just the investment portfolio our policy and operating committee – consisting of senior members from the investment team client service operations technology and compliance areas – meets monthly to discuss issues that may impact our clients and our business with members from every department working together we have created a flexible streamlined and open system of internal communication that undeniably leads to better results for our clients client service  report from its beginnings hillview employed a business model rooted in clientcentricity – it is embedded deep within the every fabric of our firm’s governance management practices and compensation structures the firm’s high employeetoclient ratio helps to provide a dedicated diligent service team for each of our clients each team is led by one of the firm’s partners and includes a financial planning associate who handles daytoday responsibilities and tasks resulting from client interactions and a portfolio administrator responsible for all operational functions service includes timely systematic client communication and informative meetings throughout the year we are leaders in the efficient use technology – leveraging it to enhance the client experience increase the value of our service and deepen our relationships the hillview client portal offers a performancereporting platform that aggregates information on all of a client’s investments providing portfoliowide visibility regardless of where assets are held our clients get a comprehensive view of their assets while we analyze and monitor all of their investments – enabling us to make betterinformed recommendations and advise them in a holistic manner the portal is password protected and available  providing a reliable and insightful tool for our clients to view their investments information on all liquid investments is available on a dailybasis and less liquid investments on a monthlyquarterly basis clients may also store important documents and personal information in their document vault in times of emergency they can count on knowing there is one secure location to access all the information they need hillview capital advisors llc your challenges who we are  what we do hillview capital advisors llc is a premier provider of financial advisory services to wealth creators their families and foundations since our founding we have been leaders in employing an open architecture approach to financial management we provide a full range of capabilities associated with a dedicated family office as well as the benefits associated with a large wealth management firm scaled to deliver a differentiated client experience the firm is focused on providing comprehensive wealth management solutions that are objective free of conflict and customized to the individual needs and aspirations of each client your wealth services wealth management hillview provides a full range of capabilities associated with a dedicated family office one of our differentiating characteristics in the industry is our approach to creating customized solutions for clients our focus on the delivery of holistic planning services—a deep understanding of a… read more… relevant cases outsourced cio at hillview we understand the investment challenges that face institutional clients for almost two decades we have offered foundations and endowments customized asset management solutions that are aligned with each organization’s unique mission performance objectives and management… read more… relevant cases philanthropic advisory service at hillview we engage our clients in valuebased conversations about philanthropy early on in our relationship this is to clearly understand their intentions assess all available options analyze the benefits and potentials of each element and finally create a customtailored plan… read more… relevant cases relevant cases your goals process  investment philosophy hillview’s investment philosophy represents the 